<%

latest_event = data.events.events.first
latest_event_date = Chronic.parse(latest_event.date)
is_event_upcoming = ((latest_event_date + latest_event.duration*60*60) > Time.now)

%>
<section class="event-information">
  <div class="site-width twelve-columns">

    <div class="column span-four">

      <h2>When is FEL?</h2>
      <p id="next-event-text-handle">
        <% if is_event_upcoming %>
          The next Front-end London will be on <%= latest_event_date.strftime('%A, %B %-d') %> at <%= latest_event_date.strftime('%l%P') %>—<%= (latest_event_date + latest_event.duration*60*60).strftime('%-l:%M%P') %>.<br /> 
          Doors open at 6:30pm.
        <% else %>
        The next Front-end London is yet to be announced. The event usually takes place on the last Thursday of the month.
        <% end %>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="column span-four">

      <h2>What to expect</h2>
      <p>Many people say that one of the best things about Front-end London is the socialising that happens before the event and afterwards when we go to the pub.</p>

      <p>With that in mind we’d like to invite you to a bit different kind of event this month: where we do the socialising without any of the talks. Call it a drink-up if you like, but essentially we’re going to the pub and we’d love it if you could join us.</p>

    </div>

    <div class="column span-four">

      <h2>The venue</h2>

      <p class="adr">
        <span class="company">Exmouth Arms</span><br>
        <span class="street-address">
          23 Exmouth Market
        </span><br>
        <span class="region">London</span>,
        <span class="postal-code">EC1R 4QL</span>
      </p>
      <a href="https://www.google.co.uk/maps/place/Exmouth+Arms/@51.525762,-0.1097,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x0:0xdf0c653619c30112">View on Google Maps</a>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
